        "id": 1577387,
        "text": "<p>Current year balances for working capital accounts are $8 million for accounts payable, $13 million for inventory, and $10 million for accounts receivable. If the former is forecasted to grow 3% and the latter two line items are forecasted to grow 4%, an analyst will estimate a working capital total closest to:</p>",
