        "text": "<p>Todd Gregory has been recently hired as the head of compliance for Speed Capital. He decides the firm should precisely follow the recommendations of the CFA Institute Standards of Professional Conduct to ensure integrity within the firm. Which of the following is NOT a compliance procedure that Speed should put in place?</p>",
