        "text": "<p>Arthur Harrow, CFA, is a pharmaceuticals analyst at Dominion Asset Management. His supervisor directs him to prepare separate research reports on Miracle Drug Company and Wonder Drug Company. Harrow serves on the board of Miracle and owns shares of Wonder. According to the Standards of Professional Conduct, which of the following actions is Harrow required to take when he writes the research reports?</p>",
