        "text": "<p>Jacob Sands, CFA, is an investment advisor working with a client who would like to incorporate more fixed income into his investment portfolio. The client already has a significant amount of funds allocated to relatively safe investments and has asked Sands about adding distressed debt to his portfolio. Sands will most likely describe these investments as having a:</p>",
