        "text": "<p>Ashley Brown, CFA, applies for a new job. In her application letter, she states, \"As a CFA charterholder, I provide the best value in trade execution.\" Further, she states, \"I passed all three CFA Program examinations in three consecutive years.\" Has Brown violated the Standards?</p>",
