        "text": "<p>An analyst has the following data:</p><ul><li>PNS Manufacturing: Expected return 15%, Std Dev 18%, Correlation with market 75%</li><li>InCharge Travel: Expected return 11%, Std Dev 17%, Correlation with market 85%</li><li>Market Std Dev = 22%</li></ul><p>Which of the following are the betas for PNS and InCharge?</p>",
