        "text": "<p>Brian Nebrik, CFA, meets with a new investment management client. They compose a statement that defines each of their responsibilities concerning this account and choose a benchmark index with which to evaluate the account's performance. Which of these items should be included in the client's Investment Policy Statement (IPS)?</p>",
