        "correctAnswerIndex": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Globalization is the trend toward increased international integration. Nationalism involves prioritizing national interests and can lead to protectionist policies. Therefore, a decrease in nationalism promotes international cooperation and trade (globalization).</p>"
