        "text": "<p>An analyst gathers the following information:</p><table border=\"1\"><tbody><tr><td>USD/AUD spot rate</td><td>0.8027</td></tr><tr><td>AUD 1-year interest rate</td><td>3.30%</td></tr><tr><td>USD 1-year interest rate</td><td>2.42%</td></tr></tbody></table><p>USD/AUD is the amount of USD per 1 AUD.<br>Q. The USD/AUD 1-year forward rate is <i>closest to</i>:</p>",
