        "text": "<p>Given the following cash flow stream:</p><table border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>End of Year</th><th>Annual Cash Flow</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>$4,000</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>$2,000</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>-0-</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>-$1,000</td></tr></tbody></table><p>Using a 10% discount rate, the present value of this cash flow stream is:</p>",
