        "text": "<p>There is a 60% chance that the economy will be good next year and a 40% chance that it will be bad. If the economy is good, there is a 70% chance that XYZ Incorporated will have EPS of $5.00 and a 30% chance that their earnings will be $3.50. If the economy is bad, there is an 80% chance that XYZ Incorporated will have EPS of $1.50 and a 20% chance that their earnings will be $1.00. What is the firm's expected EPS?</p>",
