        "text": "<p>A survey is taken to determine whether the average starting salaries of CFA charterholders is equal to or greater than $59,000 per year. What is the test statistic given a sample of 135 newly acquired CFA charterholders with a mean starting salary of $64,000 and a standard deviation of $5,500?</p>",
